author: USA TODAY, Jazmin Goodwin, USA TODAY
title: Girl Scout Cookies are moving to online orders amid coronavirus pandemic
description: Girls Scout Cookies are now available for online order nationwide due to the coronavirus crisis.
content:
Just as the holiday overindulging ends, its time for Girl Scout cookie season. Which flavor is America's favorite? Sean Dowling (@seandowlingtv) has more.
Thin-mint cookies, anyone?
